# Visual Stability: Contextual Loading States

- NEVER leave async regions blank while data is loading.
- Use localized skeletons/placeholders that mirror the final component structure.
- Avoid full-page blocking spinners for section-level or widget-level data updates.
- Keep already rendered content interactive when a neighboring async section refreshes.

## Example

```tsx
// Good: localized fallback preserves context
<section aria-busy={isLoading}>
  {isLoading ? <OrdersTableSkeleton /> : <OrdersTable rows={rows} />}
</section>
```
